Rating: 4
Beautiful use of plums! I had a case of Elephant Heart Plums, and made a half recipe including (if you can believe it), only 1 tbsp sugar and no extra water. The wine was a light Zin. For an encore performance I substituted blueberries for the raspberries and liked it even more. I will be repeating this recipe!

